HAVING been Requeſted to Peruſe the Sermon Emitted herewith, I have done it with Satisfaction and Delight; 
                  ••
               nding it to be Solid, Savoury, Serious and Convincing: I hope it will be Effectual unto the End deſigned by the worthy Author, in permitting the Publication of it; at the deſire of ſome Piouſly diſpoſed Perſons who (I underſtand) importuned it from him.
